      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds good. Quick question though—the distance seems a bit off for a trip between Shibuya and Marunouchi? I thought they were further apart than 1.5km. Also, could you give me a more detailed breakdown of the transit options? I'll probably be using the subway most days so a quick overview of the lines would be helpful.",
